trans-unit.source: Provides design-time support for <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: Zapewnia obsługę projektowania dla <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone"> </xref> kontrolki.

trans-unit.source: ConnectionsZoneDesigner provides a design-time representation of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone> control with a menu to access the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZoneDesigner.AutoFormats%2A> collection and the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ToolZoneDesigner.ViewInBrowseMode%2A> property for the convenience of the page developer.
trans-unit.target: ConnectionsZoneDesigner zawiera reprezentację czasu projektowania <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone>kontroli dostępu do menu <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZoneDesigner.AutoFormats%2A>kolekcji i <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ToolZoneDesigner.ViewInBrowseMode%2A>Właściwości dla wygody deweloperów strony.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ToolZoneDesigner.ViewInBrowseMode%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZoneDesigner.AutoFormats%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone>

trans-unit.source: It is the only zone designer that does not support designer regions.
trans-unit.target: Jest tylko projektanta strefy, który nie obsługuje projektanta regionów.

trans-unit.source: This is because <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone> controls uses links to create connections instead of a drag-and-drop user interface (UI).
trans-unit.target: Jest to spowodowane <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone>formanty używa łącza w celu utworzenia połączenia zamiast interfejs przeciągania i upuszczania użytkownika (UI).</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZoneDesigner.AutoFormats%2A> collection and the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ToolZoneDesigner.ViewInBrowseMode%2A> property both appear on the verbs menu of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone> control.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZoneDesigner.AutoFormats%2A>Kolekcji i <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ToolZoneDesigner.ViewInBrowseMode%2A>Właściwości znajdować się w menu zleceń <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone>kontroli.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ToolZoneDesigner.ViewInBrowseMode%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZoneDesigner.AutoFormats%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZoneDesigner.AutoFormats%2A>, when selected, provides a selection of color schemes.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZoneDesigner.AutoFormats%2A>, po wybraniu zapewnia wybrane schematy kolorów.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZoneDesigner.AutoFormats%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ToolZoneDesigner.ViewInBrowseMode%2A> check box, when selected, displays the contents of the control as it would appear in the browser; the control will be empty until a connection is made.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ToolZoneDesigner.ViewInBrowseMode%2A>Pole wyboru, gdy zaznaczone, wyświetla zawartość kontrolki, podobnie jak w przeglądarce; kontrolka będzie pusty, dopóki nawiązaniu połączenia.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ToolZoneDesigner.ViewInBrowseMode%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can inherit from ConnectionsZoneDesigner to support a custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone> control as with any other control designer.
trans-unit.target: Może dziedziczyć ConnectionsZoneDesigner do obsługi niestandardowej <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone>sterować tak jak w przypadku innych projektanta formantów.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone>

trans-unit.source: You can override the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZoneDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A> method to change the markup that renders the control.
trans-unit.target: Można zastąpić <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZoneDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A>metodę, aby zmienić kod znaczników, który renderuje kontrolki.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZoneDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can also override the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZoneDesigner.AutoFormats%2A> collection to add a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection> with a custom scheme.
trans-unit.target: Możesz też przesłonić <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZoneDesigner.AutoFormats%2A>kolekcji można dodać <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection>z schematu niestandardowego.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZoneDesigner.AutoFormats%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZoneDesigner"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicjuje nowe wystąpienie klasy <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZoneDesigner"> </xref> klasy.

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of predefined automatic formatting schemes to display in the **Auto Format** dialog box for the associated control at design time.
trans-unit.target: Pobiera zbiór wstępnie zdefiniowanych automatyczne formatowanie schematy do wyświetlenia w **automatyczne formatowanie** okno dialogowe skojarzonego formantu w czasie projektowania.

trans-unit.source: The AutoFormats property overrides its base implementation to get a predefined collection that is specific to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone> class.
trans-unit.target: Właściwość autoformaty zastępuje jego podstawowa implementacja można pobrać wstępnie zdefiniowanych kolekcję, która jest specyficzna dla <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone>klasy.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone>

trans-unit.source: A predefined <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection"></xref> with a default ConnectionZone scheme.
trans-unit.target: Wstępnie zdefiniowanej <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection"> </xref> z domyślnego schematu ConnectionZone.

trans-unit.source: Gets the markup that is used to represent the control at design time.
trans-unit.target: Pobiera kod znaczników, który jest używany do reprezentowania formantu w czasie projektowania.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> that is the markup to represent the control at design time.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.String>czyli znaczników do reprezentowania formantu w czasie projektowania.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Binds the designer to the specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Wiąże projektanta do określonego <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone"> </xref> formantu.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone"></xref> control associated with the designer.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone"> </xref> Kontroli powiązanej z projektanta.

trans-unit.source: Hides a preset group of properties at design time.
trans-unit.target: Ukrywa grupę predefiniowanych właściwości w czasie projektowania.

trans-unit.source: The PreFilterProperties method overrides the parent method to hide the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone.EmptyZoneTextStyle%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone.PartChromeStyle%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone.PartStyle%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone.PartTitleStyle%2A> properties in the designer.
trans-unit.target: Metoda PreFilterProperties zastępuje metodę nadrzędną ukrycia <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone.EmptyZoneTextStyle%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone.PartChromeStyle%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone.PartStyle%2A>, i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone.PartTitleStyle%2A>Właściwości w projektancie.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone.PartTitleStyle%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone.PartStyle%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone.PartChromeStyle%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone.EmptyZoneTextStyle%2A>

trans-unit.source: This is because the properties in question are not rendered by <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone> controls and are therefore not relevant.
trans-unit.target: Jest to spowodowane zagrożona właściwości nie są renderowane przez <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone>kontrolek i czy w związku z tym nieistotne.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Collections.IDictionary> of the set of properties associated with the control.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.IDictionary>Zestawu właściwości skojarzone z formantem.</xref:System.Collections.IDictionary>
